                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">It encompasses day to day teaching plans, activities
                                    with
                                    clearly defined objectives.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card mb-4 text-center border-2 shadow-sm wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s"
