                            <div class="card-body py-4 px-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">TEACHING WITH PHONIC SOUNDS</h6>
                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">Through the phonic sound system, our kindergarten
                                    children
                                    can easily read the letters, sentences and paragraphs. Even blended words like ch,
                                    sh,
                                    bl etc. are easily taught.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card mb-4 text-center border-2 shadow-sm wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s"
                            style="background-color: rgba(250, 245, 220, 0.9); border-color: #29abe2 !important; border-radius: 15px 0 15px 0 !important;">
                            <div class="card-body py-4 px-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">CONFIDENCE BUILDING AND STAGE
                                    EXPOSURE
                                </h6>
                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">Different competitions are organized to boost the
                                    confidence
                                    of children and help them overcome stage fear.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card mb-4 text-center border-2 shadow-sm wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.7s"
                            style="background-color: rgba(250, 245, 220, 0.9); border-color: #662d91 !important; border-radius: 15px 0 15px 0 !important;">
                            <div class="card-body py-4 px-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">PRACTICAL KNOWLEDGE OF SURROUNDING
                                </h6>
                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">Display board, teaching aids, sports, art, activities
                                    and
                                    trips with particular themes are organized.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <!-- Column 2 -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-5">

                        <div class="card mb-4 text-center border-2 shadow-sm wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s"
                            style="background-color: rgba(250, 245, 220, 0.9); border-color: #ed1c24 !important; border-radius: 15px 0 15px 0 !important;">
                            <div class="card-body py-4 px-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">HAPPY CHILDREN, HAPPY PARENTS</h6>
                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">Lighter school bags, only two books in the bag. Books
                                    are
                                    replaced after 21 days.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card mb-4 text-center border-2 shadow-sm wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s"
                            style="background-color: rgba(250, 245, 220, 0.9); border-color: #662d91 !important; border-radius: 15px 0 15px 0 !important;">
                            <div class="card-body py-4 px-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">VALUE BASED EDUCATION</h6>
                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">Children are given value based education by involving
                                    them
                                    in the celebration of festivals like Baisakhi, Holi, Diwali, Christmas, Guruparv,
                                    EID
                                    etc.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card mb-4 text-center border-2 shadow-sm wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s"
                            style="background-color: rgba(250, 245, 220, 0.9); border-color: #ed1c24 !important; border-radius: 15px 0 15px 0 !important;">
                            <div class="card-body py-4 px-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">EXAM IN FRONT OF PARENTS</h6>
                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">100 Days celebration is organized during mid session to
                                    exhibit the academic performance of the child in front of the parents.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card mb-4 text-center border-2 shadow-sm wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.8s"
                            style="background-color: rgba(250, 245, 220, 0.9); border-color: #8cc63f !important; border-radius: 15px 0 15px 0 !important;">
                            <div class="card-body py-4 px-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">TEN THEMES</h6>
                                <p class="small text-dark mb-0">Are taken in a year according to the age level of the
                                    children. For example - Me Special, Means of Transport, Nutritious Food, Farm
                                    Animals,
                                    Wild Animals, 100 Days, Aquatic Animals, Birds, Safety, Our helpers.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
